周年的第一天,密西根僑民將於元月一日上午十一點,在美華中心廣場舉行密西根的升旗典禮(全球以美國加州時間早上八點為準),希望台灣僑民們踴躍參加,也歡迎攜帶美國當地朋友參加,升旗典禮過後,於12點籌備會將提供多種粥點,以祛寒氣,希望僑學各界能多多呼朋引友踴躍參加,也希望鼓勵年輕學子參與.\n\n時間 : 元月一日上午十一點,\n\n地點 : 美華活動中心廣場:32585 Concord Drive, Madison Hts., MI 48071\n\n有問題者可洽: 周綵玲2483208888孫絡典5868263936\n\n<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Holidays Break</span></strong>\n\nThere will be no school for 12/25/2010 and 1/1/2011, due to holidays break. We  wish your family the gifts of joy, good health and peace this  season. We wish you warm wonderful times with family and friends and  much love. We look forward to exciting and challenging new learning  experiences in the 2011 New Year!','MCS Newsletter     Dec. 18, 2010',0,'','inherit','open','open','','116-revision','','','2010-12-16 18:10:06','2010-12-16 22:10:06','',116,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=117',0,'revision','',0);
